{"tid":48690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"街頭毆鬥3少女 3休班警被捕","createTime":"2016-12-21T08:20:20.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T08:55:53.000Z","uid":12670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"985ea38e94335df6fe650eb13af77f5b97ff2787","tid":48690,"uid":12670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:20:20.000Z","msg":"3名休班警涉嫌酒後在街頭與3名少女毆鬥，事後全部人被捕。事發於凌晨3時半左右，4名休班警員，在旺角夜店消遣後帶醉離開，至旺角道28號對開，疑與3名同為22歲的少女踫撞後，一名少女感覺被人觸摸臀部，大怒與其中3警爭執，雙方繼而大打出手，眾人均手部受傷。警方接報到場調查，以涉嫌在公眾地方打架將6人拘捕，全部人事後被送廣華醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n有請休班警巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6b068b49bf42fd9300117b87a3d1994a7eb9f0b","tid":48690,"uid":12670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:29:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83911d82f4ec81a2c75aed10b95ce036eb76f527","tid":48690,"uid":12670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:55:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}